<p class="p1">Nicholas Sims-Williams, Frantz Grenet, and &Eacute;tienne de la Vaissi&egrave;re, &ldquo;The Sogdian Ancient Letter V,&rdquo; <em>Bulletin of the Asia Institute</em> 12, 1998, pp. 91-104.</p>
